  "title": "Facilities Officer",
  "description": "<p>•\nConduct routine inspections and preventive maintenance of electrical systems.\nair-conditioning, plumbing, fire protection systems, and AV equipment.</p><p>\n• Perform minor repairs and maintenance, including replacing light tubes,\nswitches, taps, valves, locks, and sanitary fixtures.</p><p>\n• Carry out basic building repairs such as painting, plastering, patching\npartitions, and simple cement works.</p><p>\n• Handle basic carpentry and ironmongery tasks, including fabricating shelves,\nfixing panels, and replacing door hardware.</p><p>\n• Supervise and coordinate service contractors (cleaning, landscaping, pest\ncontrol, repair vendors) to ensure safe and quality work.</p><p>\n• Prepare, operate, and troubleshoot AV equipment for events and assist with\nevent support and logistics.</p><p>\n• Manage administrative tasks like recording utility readings, tracking\ninventories, handling maintenance requests, and following up on work orders.</p><p>\n• Participate in physical site duties, including moving furniture/equipment,\nsite walkabouts, and supporting office or accommodation moves.</p>",
